            <span style="color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5rem;">&plus;</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 1.7; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; cursor: default; font-size: 1.05rem;">
            Highly family-friendly. In fact, it is very popular with domestic Saudi families in the summer who travel here specifically to escape the heat. You will find numerous parks, family-oriented festivals, cable car rides, and safe hiking trails suitable for children of all ages.
